 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Remote Position - Digital Marketing Manager QuanticMind, Inc. Remote Remote Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Do you excel at digital marketing and thrive working with data in a fast-paced startup environment? QuanticMind Digital is looking for passionate candidates with demonstrated digital marketing industry expertise who enjoy working with industry-leading clients from around the country. At QuanticMind, you'll also be joining one of the fastest-growing companies in the marketing technology world. 
The ideal candidate is a self-starter, loves a challenge, and has a passion for learning. To be successful, the Digital Marketing Manager must have the ability to think strategically and be comfortable working in a fast-paced environment. This person must be able to analyze performance/data and evaluate to determine the best course of action across multiple clients at once. 
Responsibilities: 
Hands-on campaign creation, uploading, reporting, and optimization of client accounts. 
Conversion rate optimization and testing - you'll have help making the changes, but you have the opportunity to drive the testing strategy. 
