Communicate - As a strategic resource to clients, provide strategic recommendations and perspective on client performance. 
Requirements: 
A Bachelor's degree is required 
A minimum of five years experience leading and managing digital advertising campaigns, including search engine marketing 
Proven experience in a similar position, including demonstrated expertise in using digital marketing best practices to achieve performance goals 
About QuanticMind: 
